#. Tag: author
#: configdialog.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid "<firstname>Pamela</firstname> <surname>Robert</surname>"
msgstr "<firstname>Pamela</firstname> <surname>Robert</surname>"

#. Tag: email
#: configdialog.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "pamroberts@blueyonder.co.uk"
msgstr "pamroberts@blueyonder.co.uk"

#. Tag: trans_comment
#: configdialog.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "ROLES_OF_TRANSLATORS"
msgstr "ULOGE_PREVODILACA"

#. Tag: title
#: configdialog.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &sheets; Configuration Dialog Box"
msgstr "&sheets; Konfiguracijski dijaloški okvir"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem> Configure "
"&sheets;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> opens a dialog box with several "
"pages, selected with the icons at the left of the dialog box, which allow "
"you to change many aspects of &sheets;'s operation."
msgstr ""
"Odabiranjem <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem> "
"Konfiguriraj &sheets;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> otvara dijaloški okvir "
"sa više stranica,označenih sa ikonama na lijevoj strani dijaloškog okvira, "
"koji vam dozvoljava da promijenite mnoge aspekte operacija &sheets;-a ."

#. Tag: title
#: configdialog.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface"
msgstr "Interfejs"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configdialog.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Configuration."
msgstr "Konfiguracija interfejsa."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor movement after pressing Enter:"
msgstr "Pokret kursora nakon pritiskanja Enter-a:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select whether pressing the &Enter; key will move the cursor <guilabel>Down</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Up</guilabel>, <guilabel>Right</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Left</guilabel>, <guilabel>Down, First Column</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>None</guilabel> as determined by the setting in this drop down "
"selection box."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite pritiskanjem &Enter; tipke će pomjeriti kursor <guilabel>Dole</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Gore</guilabel>, <guilabel>Desno</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Lijevo</guilabel>, <guilabel>Dole, Prva kolona</guilabel> ili "
"<guilabel>Nijedna</guilabel> kao što je određeno postavkama u padajućoj "
"listi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Function shown in the status bar:"
msgstr "Funkcija prikazana u statusnoj traci:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This drop down selection box can be used to choose the calculation performed "
"by the <link linkend=\"statusbarsum\">Statusbar Summary </link> function."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj odabir može biti korišten za izbor proračuna koje obavlja <link linkend="
"\"statusbarsum\">Sumacija statusne trake</link> funkcija."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unit:"
msgstr "Jedinica:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose the default unit that will be used in your sheets."
msgstr "Odaberite podrazumijevanu jedinicu za vaše tablice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation step:"
msgstr "Ubacivanje koraka:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the amount of indent that will be used in the cell when you choose the "
"<guilabel>Increase Indent</guilabel>/<guilabel>Decrease Indent</guilabel> "
"actions from the toolbar. These actions are not enabled by default in the "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite količinu sadržaja koja će biti korištena u ćeliji kada odaberete "
"<guilabel>Povećaj sadržaj</guilabel>/<guilabel>Smanji sadržaj</guilabel> "
"akcije iz alatne trake. Ove akcije nisu omogućene zadano u alatnoj traci."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Capture all navigation keys while editing"
msgstr "Dohvati navigacijske tastere pri izmjeni"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Captures all navigation keys, &ie; the arrow keys, page up/down, tabulator "
"and backward tabulator key, while editing a cell with the embedded editor. "
"The embedded editor is the one appearing directly in the cell. If captured, "
"these keys are used for navigating in the editor. Otherwise, they are used "
"for cell navigation."
msgstr ""
"Uzima sve navigacijske tipke &ie; strelice, stranica gore/dole, tabulator i "
"nazad tabulator tipku, doku uređujete ćeliju sa uređivačem. Ugrađeni "
"uređivač je onaj koji se pojavi direktno u ćeliji. Ako su snimljene ove "
"tipke se koriste ua navigaciju u uređivaču. U suprotnom, koriste se za "
"kretanje kroz ćelije."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Colors</guilabel> section lets you choose the color of the "
"sheet grid. If you do not want the grid to appear at all, uncheck the "
"<guilabel>Show grid</guilabel> box in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sheet</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Sheet Properties</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Boje</guilabel> odjeljak vam dozvoljava odabir boje za stranicu. "
"Ako ne želite da se ivica pojavi odznačite <guilabel>Prikaži linije</"
"guilabel> u <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sveska</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Postavke sveske</guimenuitem></menuchoice> okviru."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section also lets you select the color of the lines used to indicate "
"the printed page borders when the <guimenuitem>Page Borders</guimenuitem> "
"box in the <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu is checked."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj odjeljak također dozvoljava da odaberete boju linija korištenih za "
"prikaz ivica stranice pri printanju kada je <guimenuitem>Ivice stranice</"
"guimenuitem> u <guimenu>Pregled</guimenu> meniju označen."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Custom</guilabel> from the current color to display the "
"standard &kde; <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite <guilabel>Uređeno</guilabel> u odabranoj boji da se prikaže "
"standardni &kde; <guilabel>Odaberi boju</guilabel> okvir."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grid"
msgstr "Ivica"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click here to change the grid color &ie; the color of the borders of each "
"cell."
msgstr "Pritisnite da odaberete boju ivica &ie; boja okvira svake ćelije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page border"
msgstr "Okvir strane"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Page Borders</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item is checked, the page borders are "
"displayed. Click here to choose another color for the borders than the "
"default red."
msgstr ""
"Kada je <menuchoice><guimenu>Pregled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži okvir "
"stranice</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ikona označena, prikazane su boje okvira "
"stranice. Pritisnite ovdje da odaberete drugu boju okvira jer je zadana "
"crvena."

#. Tag: title
#: configdialog.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open/Save"
msgstr "Otvori/spremi"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configdialog.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open/Save Configuration."
msgstr "Otvori/spremi podešavanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of entries in Recent Files list:"
msgstr "Broj ulazaka u listu posljednjih dokumenata:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Controls the maximum number of filenames that are shown when you select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu> Open Recent</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Kontroliše maksimalan broj imena dokumenata koja su prikazana kada odaberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Dokument</guimenu><guisubmenu> Otvori nedavno</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autosave interval:"
msgstr "Interval automatskog spremanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can select the time between autosaves, or disable this feature "
"altogether by choosing <guilabel>No autosave</guilabel> (by selecting the "
"minimum value)."
msgstr ""
"Ovdje odabirete vrijeme između automatskih spremanja ili onemogućujete ovaj "
"dodatak zajedno sa izborom <guilabel>Bez automatskog spremanja</guilabel> "
"(odabirom minimalne vrijednosti)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create backup file:"
msgstr "Stvori rezervni dokument:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box if you want some backup files created. This is checked per "
"default."
msgstr ""
"Popunite ovu kućicu ako želite da se prave rezervne datoteke. Ovo je "
"podrazumjevano popunjeno."

#. Tag: title
#: configdialog.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins"
msgstr "Dodaci"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configdialog.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins Configuration."
msgstr "Podešavanja dodataka."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check a plugin in the list to enable it. Display the <guilabel>About</"
"guilabel> dialog by clicking the info button at the right side of the list "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Provjerite dodatak ako ga želite omogućiti. Prikažite <guilabel>O</guilabel> "
"okvir pritiskom na info tipku na desnoj strani s liste."

#. Tag: title
#: configdialog.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spelling"
msgstr "Provjera pravopisa"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configdialog.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spell Checker Configuration."
msgstr "Podešavanje provjere pravopisa."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "This page lets you configure the behavior of &sheets;'s spell checker."
msgstr ""
"Ova stranica vam omogućava podešavanje ponašanja  &sheets; provjere "
"pravopisa."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information please refer to the <ulink url=\"help:kcontrol/"
"spellchecking\">Spell Checker</ulink> documentation."
msgstr ""
"Za više pogledati <ulink url=\"help:kcontrol/spellchecking\">Provjera "
"pravopisa</ulink> dokumentaciju."

#. Tag: title
#: configdialog.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "Author"
msgstr "Automatski pokretač"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configdialog.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Author Configuration."
msgstr "Podešavanja automatskog pokretača."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose an author profile for your document."
msgstr "Izaberite profil automatskog pokretača za vaš dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add a new profile or delete the current profile using the buttons to "
"the right of the profiles drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Možete dodati novi profil ili izbrisati trenutni korištenjem tipki sa desne "
"strane padajuće liste."
